    "description": "<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Requirements:</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">you must have mastered the </span><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Dancer </span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Class.</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">At the start of your turn during a conflict, if you have <strong>no </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>martial armor </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">equipped, you may spend 1 Fabula Point to immediately perform<strong> </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>up to three different dances </strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">among those you know, in the order you prefer and without paying their MP cost. If you do, you </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>cannot perform dances in any way</strong> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">until the end of your next turn.</span> </p>",
